South Africa's Gordhan to Brief Reporters on New Treasury Director-General

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-20T07:26:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/south-africa-s-gordhan-to-brief-reporters-on-new-treasury-director-general.html
South African Finance Minister
 Pravin Gordhan  will brief reporters today on the appointment of
a new director-general for the National Treasury.  The briefing will be held in  Pretoria  at 2:30 p.m. local
time, the government said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  